- class within another class
- nested class

Types:
 1. Member inner class
	- a class created within a class but outside the method

 2. Anonymous Inner class
    - class without name
      a) class (abstract or concrete class)
      b) interface

 3. Local Inner class
    - can not be invoked from outside the method

 4. Static inner class


Homework:
1. Advantages/Disadvantages of Inner class